      "rationale": "The CFD solver (ANSYS Fluent 2023R2) is subject to a full ISO 9001-compliant software quality management plan including version-controlled source, automated regression test suite (>2400 test cases), documented release notes, and a site-specific installation qualification (IQ) and operational qualification (OQ) protocol executed at the performing laboratory. All simulation scripts and post-processing macros are stored in a Git repository with signed commits, and a dedicated software validation report (SVR-CFD-2023-07) was reviewed and approved by an independent quality engineer. No open defects affecting hemolysis prediction pathways were identified at time of study execution.",
