        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "GCI on production mesh must be < 5% for NIH QoI. Asymptotic convergence ratio must be within 5% of unity. Wall y+ < 5 on hemolysis-critical surfaces. Achieved: GCI = 1.8%, ratio = 1.001, y+ < 1.0."
