        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Hemolysis constitutive model selected via documented comparison of ≥ 3 candidate models with quantitative selection criterion. Turbulence model sensitivity < 10% on primary QoI. Non-Newtonian effects assessed. Achieved: 8 models compared, Bayesian selection, turbulence sensitivity 4.8%, non-Newtonian effect 7.9% (retained)."
